#

Hearty Beef Stew with Root Vegetables

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Tags:

comfort foodheartystew

Description

A comforting, robust stew featuring tender beef and a medley of flavorful root vegetables, perfect for warming up on a chilly day.

Ingredients

  • beef chuck roast: 2 lbs
  • carrots: 4, chopped
  • potatoes: 3, diced
  • onion: 1, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • beef broth: 4 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tbsp
  • bay leaves: 2
  • thyme: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
